Story:

Chon is suffered from having bad times while sleeping. He tries not to sleep because he\&#039;s scared of a girl in his nightmares. In the dreams, the girl screams for help before she is cruelly killed. Ae, Chon\&#039;s sister is worried about the illusion that Chon sees in his dreams, so she introduces him to a psychiatrist. Chon tries to prove that what he sees is not just the illusion. Finally, Chon is right when some clues in his nightmares lead him to a morgue number 19. And now, the story of the dead body inside the morgue is gradually revealed.
